{"TopicId":212784,"ForumId":136,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;Auto: Orbital/Ground\u0026quot; messages blocking screen","CreatedByName":"Sledder10","CreatedById":226364,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T21:30:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sledder10","CreatedById":226364,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T21:30:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpon a low Mun orbit, I get this spam of messages blocking the screen. If I pause time, they all go away after a moment. But upon starting time again, they immediately pop back up.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u00220?ui=2\u0026amp;ik=1f14778e37\u0026amp;attid=0.1\u0026amp;permmsgid=msg-a:r2794432127181833387\u0026amp;th=1868a792e531635e\u0026amp;view=fimg\u0026amp;fur=ip\u0026amp;sz=s0-l75-ft\u0026amp;attbid=ANGjdJ_BVAwcuasJoGYkvvXup4VcKEkpH0FyN5K7wYpNDFZTWH_-1tgAD-9cmt89_sLRde5Lq08TshjhFngNGxZwu_esAUqz9eY1gAPy7hrMt_KzT_gA-yD4mGvZeVk\u0026amp;disp=emb\u0026amp;realattid=1868a78efc0675c89331\u0022 src=\u0022https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0?ui=2\u0026amp;ik=1f14778e37\u0026amp;attid=0.1\u0026amp;permmsgid=msg-a:r2794432127181833387\u0026amp;th=1868a792e531635e\u0026amp;view=fimg\u0026amp;fur=ip\u0026amp;sz=s0-l75-ft\u0026amp;attbid=ANGjdJ_BVAwcuasJoGYkvvXup4VcKEkpH0FyN5K7wYpNDFZTWH_-1tgAD-9cmt89_sLRde5Lq08TshjhFngNGxZwu_esAUqz9eY1gAPy7hrMt_KzT_gA-yD4mGvZeVk\u0026amp;disp=emb\u0026amp;realattid=1868a78efc0675c89331\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"malkuth","CreatedById":57414,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T02:24:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHit V usually clear it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Machinosaure","CreatedById":155968,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T04:07:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224243163\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212784\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677378258\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022malkuth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/25/2023 at 9:24 PM, malkuth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHit V usually clear it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I was looking for that answer too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like on low orbits the game isn\u0027t able to figure out if it should use Auto Orbital view or Auto Surface view and it going back and forth, spamming message boxes, while V overrides it with one of the new custom camera views.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Orealus","CreatedById":227505,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-07T12:44:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI reported this to support along with a screenshot and video clip.\u00A0 It\u0027s good to know about the \u0027V\u0027, I\u0027ll try that later.\u00A0 Maybe the code should have some sort of hysteresis condition so that it switches to surface under a certain threshold that is lower than when it switches to orbit.\u00A0 Perhaps that\u0027s already in place but the difference between the two thresholds isn\u0027t sufficiently large.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PTNLemay","CreatedById":30142,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-26T01:03:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust tried to land on the Mun, I can confirm this issue is still present.\u00A0 \u00A0The whole... \u0022Things explode when you undock\u0022 are also present, unfortunately.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}